highlights.text: “No Frauds” by Nicki Minaj, Drake, and Lil Wayne is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #62.
“I Don’t Wanna Live Forever (Fifty Shades Darker)” by ZAYN and Taylor Swift has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 12 weeks straight.
Ed Sheeran has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “Shape of You” is the highest at #1.
“Swalla (feat. Nicki Minaj & Ty Dolla $ign)” by Jason Derulo, Nicki Minaj, and Ty Dolla $ign is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 62 spots at #67.
